				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-V%C5%A9/Bi%E1%BB%87t-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-P7Bf9LD3ffKZk0YW45pkRg">Biệt thi kỳ 2 - 別詩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-V%C5%A9/author-A1qWp2TVE713T9GYde49XQ">Tô Vũ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Huy%E1%BB%85n/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-li%E1%BB%85u-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-12/poem-tKnn1K6xuiCLpBF3VdgkBA">Dương liễu từ kỳ 12 - 柳枝辭其十二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Huy%E1%BB%85n/author-PbzSOCmqBMTC0GXwXGPRrw">Từ Huyễn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/%C4%90%E1%BB%99-Nh%C6%B0-Thi%E1%BA%BFt-thu%E1%BB%B7/poem-pwttF1AVffdiUDEU6n0CPQ">Độ Như Thiết thuỷ - 渡如鐵水</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%9Bi-Th%C3%BAc-Lu%C3%A2n/Giang-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-c%E1%BB%91-nh%C3%A2n-ng%E1%BA%ABu-t%E1%BA%ADp-kh%C3%A1ch-x%C3%A1/poem-LwXo33-TfrHXDWZRggKPGw">Giang hương cố nhân ngẫu tập khách xá - 江鄉故人偶集客舍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%9Bi-Th%C3%BAc-Lu%C3%A2n/author-LcWycoFkFlNGUZU5U9sHSA">Đới Thúc Luân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A0nh-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-H%C3%B9ng/L%E1%BB%99/poem-FwxfT0d_OcanMENaQOo6jg">Lộ - 露</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A0nh-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-H%C3%B9ng/author-Qv7b3I2-XwrqaKCUV_nCCg">Thành Ngạn Hùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Ng%C3%B4-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-uwRnr6USqZoH4lY2BvnRfg">Ngô Châu - 梧州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Qu%E1%BB%B3-Ch%C3%A2u-ca-th%E1%BA%ADp-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-8/poem-kqewhUMwERpMDPP3NLXuXg">Quỳ Châu ca thập tuyệt cú kỳ 8 - 夔州歌十絕句其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%C3%B4-m%E1%BB%99-v%C5%A9/poem-h0jytt0r16CA91mIbSZ8GQ">Thương Ngô mộ vũ - 蒼梧暮雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95-t%C3%ADch-k%E1%BB%B3-2-T%E1%BB%91ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-gia/poem-M-50xx2ow4YFv2TP3AmR1w">Vịnh hoài cổ tích kỳ 2 - Tống Ngọc gia - 詠懷古跡其二－宋玉家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ng%E1%BB%B1-h%C3%A0-v%C3%A3n-di%E1%BB%83u/poem-fKHLviN-BZuol13fe8GXQQ">Xuân nhật, ngự hà vãn diểu - 春日御河晚眺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
